@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bttiyn(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.abs((v1 + 0.86 / v2 + 1.00)))
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.abs(v0))
    v2 = v1
    v1 = (((v0 + 0.03 / v0 + 0.12) - (v1 + 0.12 + v0 + 0.61)) / ((v1 + 0.96 - v2 + 0.55) - (v0 + 0.01 - v2 + 0.18)))
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.abs(wp.exp(v0 + 0.27)))
    v1 = wp.cos((wp.abs(v2 + 0.14) * (tmp + 0.13 - v1 + 0.02)))
    data[tid] = v0
